[{"id":"26a1291a5eaa3f16b5d6754f7d1edbf7","from":"Lesley Groff","from_email":"lesley@nysgllc.com","to":"J. Epstein","to_list":[{"name":"J. Epstein","email":"jeeproject@yahoo.com"}],"cc_list":[],"subject":"FW: Dr. Victor and LipoTherm on Fox 5 10pm News Tonight","date":"2008-05-20T12:48:21.000Z","formatted_date":"May 20, 2008","formatted_time":"12:48 PM","body":" \n\n \n\nFrom: RhodesVictor@aol.com [mailto:RhodesVictor@aol.com] \nSent: Monday, May 19, 2008 10:03 AM\nCc: RhodesVictor@aol.com\nSubject: Dr. Victor and LipoTherm on Fox 5 10pm News Tonight\n\n \n\nHello,\n\n \n\nFox 5 News filmed a segment on me and the latest technology in laser\nassisted fat reduction and skin tightening - LipoTherme.  This is the\nnewest technology available in the US and I am the first doctor to be\nperforming this procedure in the US.  It's perfect just in time for the\nunofficial launch of Summer (Memorial Day!).  Please feel free to watch\nthe segment on Fox 5 News at 10pm tonight.\n\n \n\nSincerely,\nSteven Victor, M.D.\nVICTOR DERMATOLOGY AND REJUVENATION\nVICTOR PRODUCTS INC\nTel: 212-249-3050\nFax: 212-249-1482\nCell: 917-459-8252\nRhodesVictor@aol.com\nwww.stevenvictormd.com <http://www.stevenvictormd.com/> \nwww.stevenvictormdmedispa.com\n\n\n\n\n\n________________________________\n\nWondering what's for Dinner Tonight? Get new twists on family favorites\nat AOL Food\n<http://food.aol.com/dinner-tonight?NCID=aolfod00030000000001> .\n\n","body_html":"<html xmlns:v=\"urn:schemas-microsoft-com:vml\" xmlns:o=\"urn:schemas-microsoft-com:office:office\" xmlns:w=\"urn:schemas-microsoft-com:office:word\" xmlns:m=\"http://schemas.microsoft.com/office/2004/12/omml\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/TR/REC-html40\">\n\n<head>\n<META HTTP-EQUIV=\"Content-Type\" CONTENT=\"text/html; charset=us-ascii\">\n<meta name=Generator content=\"Microsoft Word 12 (filtered medium)\">\n<!--[if !mso]>\n<style>\nv\\:* {behavior:url(#default#VML);}\no\\:* {behavior:url(#default#VML);}\nw\\:* {behavior:url(#defa